<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jạylk yạ yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (jạy lk yạ yswʿ msẖtạq ạ̉tgẖyr
 fy ạ̹ydy qywd mhmwm mtḥyr)2
 sẖkẖṣk wḥdh hw ạlly ygẖyr .. wlạ ywm ạ̹blys yạ̉sr wyʿyr
 ạlqrạr- (wḥdk yạ yswʿ .. trfʿ kl ạlạ̉tʿạb
 dmk yạ yswʿ .. mrsẖwsẖ ʿly̱ ạlạ̉ʿtạb)2
 ʿly̱ ạlmạḍy ndws .. nksr ʿndk ạ̉ṭyạb
 2- (ạ̉sjd wạ̉rkʿ yạ yswʿ qdạmk
 wạ̉nạ zy fṭym yjry lạ̉ḥḍạnk)2
 ṭʿm ạlḥryẗ hạdwq wslạmk .. ḥạss bạ̉mạn yrwyny ḥnạnk
 3- (ạ̉htf lạsmh wạ̉rfʿ lh nsẖydy
 ḥqh fy qlby slṭạnh fy ạ̹ydy)2
 nlt ạlḥryẗ ạlywm ywm ʿydy .. qlby frḥạn msrwr bygẖny</lyrics>
<hymn_number>103</hymn_number>
<author>mnạl smyr ḥnạ, mnạl smyr ḥnạ</author>
</song>